channel.title: Seriously, how to make myself admin in 525?
channel.description:
Okay call me noob or quote me,I know how to do it in 508s and 317s where you just go into character logs, but I just downloaded Berky-scape and everything is way different, I went into "io" and changed his name to mine and still didnt work, i dont think the compiling is working tho because its saying this.
javac: file not found: *.java Usage: javac <options> <source files> use -help for a list of possible options Finished! Press any key to continue . . .
but his compiler was saying could not be found so i replaced it with my 508 one.
and yeah i think berky is 508 but its hd so w/e, im calling it 525.
